OL,3,CMurderer jailed for life after killing
OL,4,Cneighbour over #60 debt
OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for life after
OL,7,Fadmitting she murdered her neighbour
OL,8,Fwhen she attacked him in a Newcastle
OL,9,Fstreet.
OL,11,FOn 11 November 2024, Brenda Heslop
OL,12,Fstabbed John Hardy, 68, at an address
OL,13,Fon Sceptre Place, in the Elswick Area.
OL,15,FNewcastle Crown Court heard that
OL,16,FHeslop, 63, believed she was owed #60
OL,17,Ffrom Mr Hardy after loaning him some
OL,18,Fmoney.
