OL,6,FMr Hardy's family said: "Our lovely
OL,7,Fbrother John was tragically taken from
OL,8,Fus and is truly missed every day by
OL,9,Fall his family and friends. We live
OL,10,Fwith this nightmare every day and our
OL,11,Flives are changed forever.
OL,13,F"We would like to thank his friends
OL,14,Fand neighbours who were there at the
OL,15,Ftime and who went to his aid to give
OL,16,Fhim comfort in his final moments.
