OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FChief Inspector Mark Atherton, of
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police's Major
OL,9,FInvestigation Team (MIT), said: "(Mr
OL,10,FHardy) was killed in one of the
OL,11,Fcruellest ways possible and our hope
OL,12,Fis that now his murderer has been
OL,13,Fjailed those who were closest to him
OL,14,Fare able to take some degree of
OL,15,Fclosure following the ordeal they have
OL,16,Fbeen through in recent months.
